wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cmat_ireland_ivors_interview_new_album-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cmat_ireland_ivors_interview_new_album-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cmat_ireland_ivors_interview_new_album-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cmat_ireland_ivors_interview_new_album-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cmat_ireland_ivors_interview_new_album-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a>向<em>NME</em>讲述了她的祖国爱尔兰令人印象深刻的文化足迹，以及她下一张专辑的计划——这张专辑可能比你想象的更早到来。</p><p>席亚拉·玛丽-爱丽丝·汤普森 (Ciara Mary-Alice Thompson) 本周（5 月 23 日星期四）在伦敦 Ivor Novellos 的红地毯上向我们发表讲话，她凭借广受好评的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/cmat-crazymad-for-me-review-lyrics-tracklist-3512398">Crazymad, For Me</a> 》获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-sampha-yussef-dayes-lead-2024-ivor-novello-nominations-3749859">最佳专辑提名</a>，但她已经确信她由于她面临的竞争，她不会获胜。该奖项后来由尤瑟夫·达耶斯 (Yussef Dayes) 领取。</p><p> “ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lankum">Lankum</a>获得了该奖项的提名，他们已经在年度爱尔兰专辑中击败了我，还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">RAYE</a> ，他在全英音乐奖上获得了 7500 万个奖项，而我只是坐在那里，摆弄我的拇指，没有赢得任何东西，”汤普森告诉 N<em>我</em>。 “所以，我的希望很低，但也很高，因为我在这里！即使获得提名也是梦想成真。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7bJm21KkU0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; j