他。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-yussef-dayes-and-skepta-and-more-win-at-2024-ivor-novello-awards-3759013">请在此处查看 2024 年 Ivor Novellos 获奖者的完整名单</a>。当晚的其他亮点包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-bruce-springsteens-full-ivors-speech-while-i-was-stone-cold-born-in-the-barrels-of-the-usa-at-16-i-desperately-yearned-to-be-british-3759240">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 荣获艾弗奖学金 (Ivor Fellowship Award)</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-paul-mccartneys-full-roasting-of-bruce-springsteen-from-the-ivors-2024-3759277">保罗·麦卡特尼爵士 (Sir Paul McCartney) 的严厉批评</a>）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-interview-lasso-ivor-novellos-country-reading-leeds-3759161">拉娜·德雷 (Lana Del Rey) 荣获国际特别奖</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cmat-interview-ireland-new-music-ivors-album-3759488">CMAT 后的文章：“爱尔兰人一直都很出色，但也有很多创伤”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
